what is children props

children props is  a special prop,Ye parent component ke andar likhe gaye content ko child component me access karne ke liye use hota hai

accessed with props.children




Need of props.children

Agar hume reusable wrapper components banana ho jaise:

Card
Modal
Button Wrapper
Layout
Container

toh har baar alag content pass karna padta hai.

Us situation me props.children use hota hai.